    <Placemark>
      <name>Kors i fjellet</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBop3WH3wogDMRhMRvR147JPb9cUR8jb-Dg3Nr7XKvdUtsogFd2pFqnC2Hy7R752wtyiaG0_lwPXfDG0JPpEDH-5xUwo1Q5M22Qn3c6NlMoV4kWJ9FzvdFzXwi1vgHKOE2W_ij-M9jmxFWs109RbEwUYaLdj_T_VJcUdrdxy5lWXsJ8PotH75O0rcpC9MmMw2N_G8_tiUH5Q3i6c?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Posisjon: 59.2377823, 9.5436826<br>Informasjon: Slike kors var det vanlig å hogge inn i nærheten av gruvene. De tjente som fastmerker, «meter riks-tegn», når gruvene skulle måles med tanke på uttatt malmmengde og skattlegging.<br>Nettside: https://photos.app.goo.gl/SkPQzkgqQ3E6zR7n6 og https://photos.app.goo.gl/ZKktL6ESvvG6rdcN9<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBorBM8Worxt0HaMDZIhHJMuaaTUM8MJfYixd8ReghAtj_axwdBJe5E6aAXUfTqn0q3zsHu1cu0ptvMVcIYu_7zMgfnAzalCx85R22ZRkun7-dtkcAdrUqAK21jGjS-y3PDvCrAzLWRxTAvkjQqD9gFOhd4ZpMNlSflbYNpfiTersUyNtSRzN_TnIc6st_ikVGfpqNmLE8yacD_U?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3ALCsBoq3WGh1nQVADhIdearqmrNVjXqHPG8mGlB--sb-7lwNpkIiR3VZWk_2xNbKGgLbrzcyQtAVprD5ITOS1JpvhkWHZa9IY7i3lHSUyZx3NJbNNi_fExGo0T2XyajBD4blhCbTPgVADpoVViZ4zq-JBE2yMP3-SAO2jkQ9zVZYho12S9dfA1cm_G1ypb8uAlqEEJKtkNph4-khgQ?fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
